| **1** | **PV-1**: Move frequency decomposition to pre-fold raw time-series, or reframe Constraint 5 claim | 2-3 days | A stellar physics reviewer WILL catch this. Applying FFT to phase-folded data is physically nonsensical for the claimed purpose. |
| **2** | **CF-1**: Reframe or fix position-aware attention's relationship to actual stellar disk position | 1-2 days | The mismatch between the paper's claim ("position on stellar disk") and the code ("position in folded time-series") will be caught by any careful reviewer. |
